sequenceDiagram
    participant Main as main.tsx
    participant BuildFunc as buildEffectiveSystemPrompt
    participant GlobalState as 全局状态
    participant API as Claude API
    Main->>BuildFunc: 启动时调用一次
    BuildFunc->>BuildFunc: 检查优先级<br/>选中最高可用
    BuildFunc->>GlobalState: setMainLoopSystemPrompt()
    GlobalState->>GlobalState: 缓存结果
    loop 每轮对话
        API->>GlobalState: 需要系统提示
        GlobalState->>API: getMainLoopSystemPrompt()
        API->>API: 使用缓存的提示
    end
    Note over GlobalState: 用户执行 /set system-prompt
    GlobalState->>GlobalState: setMainLoopSystemPrompt(新值)
    GlobalState->>API: 下一次请求使用新提示
